<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chanchin Pha phuongzak un, mihiem umna chengah,
 Mi lunggil sung lungkhamna a umna cheng ah;
 Kristien chengin thu kipahum phuongzak uhen,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung!

[V2]
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung (2)
 Van apat Thagau Thieng, Pa tiem chuh piek ei tai;
 Chanchin Pha phuongzak un, mihiem umna cheng ah,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung!

[V3]
 2. Zan sawt chuh a bei tai, taikhuo a hung vak tai,
 Lungkhamna leh thil lauhum cheng chuh a bei tai;
 Tang hawihtak apata, kawl ni no suok bangin,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung!

[V4]
 3. Lalpente Lalpen chun, sukdamna chuh nei in,
 Thagau saltangte cheng, pawtna thu A hun puoi;
 Gitloh suoka pawt ten, zawhna la hun sa'n au,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung!

[V5]
 4. I lungthim gil ahin, Hehpihna thu lien hen,
 Kumsawt lam mansakte, ma I puih theih na'ng un;
 Khawvel gitloh thimah, eihaw ei hihvak di'n,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung.

[V6]
 5. Leisiet gam kimvel ah, zie thu hi kithang hen,
 Van mi thiengte guola lei mite umna di'n;
 Hehpih tawp neilo la, haih ni um ta puona,
 Lungmuonpa A hung tung!</lyrics>
<title>THE COMFORTER HAS COME</title>
</song>